---
const techStack = ['React', 'Go', 'TypeScript', 'Node', 'Docker'];
---

<section id="about" class="site-container site-section">
  <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 items-start">
    <div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">About David Andrea</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-base-content">
        Hi, I'm Dave, a software engineer and educator based in Sydney, Nova Scotia. I design and ship full-stack web apps end-to-end—from product exploration through production-ready delivery—while building the CI/CD automations that keep them healthy.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-base-content">
        I'm just as curious about the systems around the code. I experiment with Kubernetes-based platforms to understand how teams operate at scale, and I write about how educational theory can improve how we teach coding and mathematics. Those notes often turn into engineering tutorials that demystify tooling for other developers.
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-4 text-base-content">
        <li>Builds full-stack products with Go, TypeScript, React, GraphQL, Docker, and Kubernetes</li>
        <li>Automates delivery pipelines with CI/CD and release management</li>
        <li>Writes engineering notes on modern web development and DevOps practices</li>
        <li>Publishes articles that connect educational theory and pedagogy with software development</li>
        <li>Education: University of Helsinki - 56 ECTS in modern web development and DevOps (incl. Full Stack Open certificate, 24 ECTS, plus advanced courses in DSA, TDD, Docker, Kubernetes, and a capstone web project); B.A., B.Ed., M.A.</li>
      </ul>
      <ul class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2 list-none" aria-label="Tech stack">
        {techStack.map((tech) => (
          <li class="badge badge-outline px-3 py-2 text-xs sm:text-sm lg:text-base">{tech}</li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
        <div class="stat bg-base-200 text-base-content rounded-box">
          <div class="stat-title">Years</div>
          <div class="stat-value text-primary">5+</div>
          <div class="stat-desc" style="word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal;">Building for the web</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat bg-base-200 text-base-content rounded-box">
          <div class="stat-title">Posts</div>
          <div class="stat-value text-secondary">5+</div>
          <div class="stat-desc" style="word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal;">Engineering notes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat bg-base-200 text-base-content rounded-box">
          <div class="stat-title">OSS</div>
          <div class="stat-value text-accent">10</div>
          <div class="stat-desc" style="word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal;">Projects contributed</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="card bg-base-200 text-base-content shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">What I do</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Design and deliver full-stack web applications</li>
            <li>Automate CI/CD pipelines and delivery workflows</li>
            <li>Prototype infrastructure and developer platforms with Kubernetes</li>
            <li>Write tutorials that blend educational theory with engineering practice</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
